official_title: A bill to authorize the acquisition of the Big Cypress National Fresh Water Reserve in the State of Florida.

summary.text: Authorizes the acquisition of the Big Cypress National Fresh Water Reserve in the State of Florida. Authorizes to be appropriated such sums as may be necessary to carry out this Act, but not to exceed $156,000,000 for the acquisition of lands and interests therein.

titles.title: A bill to authorize the acquisition of the Big Cypress National Fresh Water Reserve in the State of Florida.
